            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Gold please.  But the bots never give it up.  They always ask.  \r\n\r\nThis is one of the greatest games of the late 1990s.  So much fun to play again now in HD."
        },
        {
            "review_id": "225159589",
