            "review_text": "It's super fun. No game is ever the same as another game. You can play with your friends."
        },
        {
            "review_id": "227134776",
            "steam_id": "76561198064104749",
            "playtime_minutes": 4166,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "After playing through the rest of the AoE library of remakes, I've come to appreciate the \"HD\" edition a lot more. It's JUST AoE2 with some widescreen support and water bump mapping, I guess. No soulless modern UI, no \"remastered\" soundtrack. Just the experience you truly remember.\n\nWhile I mechanically find AoE2 utterly unbearable, it's a staple of the early 00's RTS genre, and I respect that, and if you want the ORIGINAL experience, this is as close as it's gonna get on modern hardware."
        },
